{"word":"ἑτοιμάζω","slug":"ἑτοιμάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑτοιμάζω</b></el> <el>(ἑτοιμάζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἑτοῖμος'><el>ἑτοῖμος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make</i> or <i>get ready, prepare, provide</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>κάπρον ἑτοιμασάτω ταμέειν</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to cause to be prepared</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἡτοίμασμαι</el>, <i>to prepare for oneself</i>, <el>τἄλλα ἡτοιμάζετο</el> <i>made his</i> other <i>arrangements</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>ἡτοιμασμένοι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to prepare oneself</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}